questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Person ; dct:subject dbc:Presidents_of_the_United_States ; dbo:activeYearsEndDate ?termEnd FILTER ( ( year(now()) - year(?termEnd) ) <= 20 ) }
